Isaiah Washington https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Isaiah_Washington 0 Isaiah Washington IV (born August 3, 1963) is an American actor. Washington appeared has Spike Lee film's Crooklyn, Clockers, Girl 6 and Get on the Bus. Washington is also known for his role as Dr. Preston Burke on the ABC medical drama television series Grey's Anatomy from 2005 until 2007, and again in 2014. From 2014 to 2018, Washington portrayed Thelonious Jaha on The CW's science fiction television series The 100. Isaiah_Washington_IV ( born August_3_,_1963 ) is an_American_actor .
